name: ReallyBored
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: i'm really bored
des: The purpose of this skill is to give ideas of what to do to the user when they indicate when they are bored. This skill provides different recommendations and a few of the responses suggest asking Alexa further questions that are not programmed into the ReallyBored skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
